== Honours ==
===Intercontinental===
* '''[[Afro-Asian Cup of Nations]]'''
** {{Silver2}} Runners-up (2): [[1987 Afro-Asian Cup of Nations|1987]], [[2007 Afro-Asian Cup of Nations|2007]]

===Continental===
* '''[[Africa Cup of Nations|CAF African Cup of Nations]]'''
** [[File:Coppa Africa.svg|22px]] '''Champions (7)''': [[1957 African Cup of Nations|1957]], [[1959 African Cup of Nations|1959]], [[1986 African Cup of Nations|1986]], [[1998 African Cup of Nations|1998]], [[2006 Africa Cup of Nations|2006]], [[2008 Africa Cup of Nations|2008]], [[2010 Africa Cup of Nations|2010]]
** [[File:Silver medal africa.svg|15px]] Runners-up (3): [[1962 Africa Cup of Nations|1962]], [[2017 Africa Cup of Nations|2017]], [[2021 Africa Cup of Nations|2021]]
** [[File:Bronze medal africa.svg|15px]] Third place (3): [[1963 Africa Cup of Nations|1963]], [[1970 Africa Cup of Nations|1970]], [[1974 Africa Cup of Nations|1974]]
* '''[[Football at the All-Africa Games|African Games]]'''{{efn|Competition organized by [[Association of National Olympic Committees of Africa|ANOCA]], officially not recognized by FIFA.}}
** [[File:Gold medal africa.svg|15px]] '''Gold medal (1)''': [[1987 All-Africa Games|1987]],[[1995 All-Africa Games|1995]]
** [[File:Bronze medal africa.svg|15px]] Bronze medal (1): [[1973 All-Africa Games|1973]]

===Regional===
* '''[[FIFA Arab Cup|Arab Cup]]'''{{efn|Official subregional competition organized and recognized by [[FIFA]] since [[2021 FIFA Arab Cup|2021]]. Previous editions were organized by [[Union of Arab Football Associations|UAFA]].}}
** {{Gold1}} '''Champions (1)''': [[1992 Arab Cup|1992]]{{efn|name="arabcup"|The [[1992 Arab Cup]] also counted as an edition of the [[Arab Games]].}}
** {{Bronze3}} Third place (1): [[1988 Arab Cup|1988]]
* '''[[Football at the Arab Games|Arab Games]]'''
** {{Gold1}} '''Gold medal (4)''': [[Football at the 1953 Arab Games|1953]], [[1965 Arab Games|1965]], [[1992 Arab Cup|1992]]{{efn|name="arabcup"}}, [[Football at the 2007 Arab Games|2007]]
** {{Silver2}} Silver medal (1): [[1961 Arab Games|1961]]
* '''[[Palestine Cup of Nations]]'''
** {{Gold1}} '''Champions (2)''': [[1972 Palestine Cup of Nations|1972]], [[1975 Palestine Cup of Nations|1975]]
* '''[[Football at the Mediterranean Games|Mediterranean Games]]'''
** {{Gold1}} '''Gold medal (1)''': [[1955 Mediterranean Games|1955]]
** {{Silver2}} Silver Medal (1): [[1951 Mediterranean Games|1951]]
** {{Bronze3}} Bronze Medal (1): [[1983 Mediterranean Games|1983]]
* '''[[Mediterranean Cup (men's football)|Mediterranean Cup]]'''
** {{Bronze3}} Third place (2): 1949, 1950–53

===Friendly===
* '''Nile Basin Tournament (1)''': [[2011 Nile Basin Tournament|2011]]
* '''[[LG Cup (association football)|LG Cup]] (1)''': [[2005 LG Cup (Egypt)|2005]]
* '''[[Friendship Tournament]] (1)''': 1994
* '''[[Korea Cup]] (1)''': [[1993 President's Cup International Football Tournament|1993]]
* '''[[Capital of Egypt Cup]] (1) ''': [[2026]]

===Awards===
* '''[[CAF Awards#African National Team of the Year|African National Team of the Year]] (3)''': 1998, 2008, 2017
* '''[[Africa Cup of Nations awards#Fair Play Award|Africa Cup of Nations Fair Play Award]] (1)''': 2017

